data.text: @PEOPLEroyals I must say I love most of your royal coverage. I do NOT love, however, that you continue to call the Duchesses of Sussex or Cambridge by their maiden names. Please honor them by at least calling them Duchess Meghan & Duchess Catherine. It really matters. Thanks!
@PEOPLEroyals No bored beyond belief with this B-Hollywood production by Meghan.
